CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier, January 8, 1955, pg. 24 reads: "New Year's Eve...was a gala night for members of the Las Catena Club who entertained their husbands and friends with a party at the home of Mr. and Mrs. Carl Talbott.  The club, aimed at charity, begins its new year by presenting a basket of food to a new Homestead mother who has ten youngsters.  Pictured are Carl Ealbott [Talbott], center; Jack Harrison, Julietta Beatty, Alcia Harrison, Earl Goodson, Florence Goodson, Chauncey Williams.  Last row: Belinda Blandberg, Milton Blandberg, Roscoe Beatty, Harriett Williams and Gloria Talbott. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Las Catena Club members with husbands and friends, including: Carl Talbott, in center; Jack Harrison, Julietta Beatty, Alcia Harrison, Earl Goodson, Florence Goodson, and Chauncey Williams; last row: Belinda Blandberg, Milton Blandberg, Roscoe Beatty, Harriett Williams, and Gloria Talbott, posed in home of Mr. and Mrs. Carl Talbott for New Year's party
